   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">This section describes the administrative tasks to be performed to set up a deal guidance process to rate deals.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
