                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">What's Covered</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">This section explains how Deal Maximizer works, how to configure it, and covers the most common use cases for administration.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Primary Audience</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
